    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<h1 id=\"id-.brikit.mobile-ParentPageforMobilePages\">Parent Page for Mobile Pages</h1>\n<p>To help you organize mobile pages, we've created a page hierarchy that separates them from desktop pages.</p>\n<p>Mobile pages you create in Theme Press 1.2 or higher nest below this page. Therefore, each space with mobile pages will have a <code>.brikit.mobile</code> page.</p>\n<p>If you created mobile pages in this space prior to 1.2, you may want to move them below this page.</p>"
    }
  },
